data.description: Beautiful home in the heart of east Orlando. Open layout. Tile and vinyl floors throughout. Granite counter tops in this large eat-in kitchen with closet pantry. Laundry closet just off the kitchen.  Garden bathtub with shower in the owner's suite. Spacious walk in closet too. The large 21'x10' rear screened porch overlooks a peaceful, county maintained pond so no rear neighbors to this fenced backyard. Roof replaced in 2014.  HVAC replaced in 2016. No homeowner's association. Just minutes from Publix, Winn-Dixie, Walmart Super Center, Waterford Lakes Town Center, so many restaurants. Easy access to Colonial Drive and Highway 408.  Let's make a deal.
